# Apps are tracked by allowlist. Everything under apps/ is ignored by default,
# so an unpublished demo can live here and build without being committed. To
# start tracking a demo, add an `!apps/<name>` line below. The directory must
# be un-ignored before its contents, so keep the `apps/*` line above the
# exceptions.
apps/*
!apps/home
!apps/cnn-playground
!apps/cnn-visualizer
!apps/cnn-architecture-comparison
!apps/cv-interpretability
